---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Container from '../components/ui/Container.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Lumina ERP consulting services. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>

  <Section background="base" padding="sm" class="pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-8 md:pb-12">
    <Container narrow>
      <h1 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-hero)] font-bold leading-[1.1] text-text-primary mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-tertiary text-sm">Last updated: February 12, 2026</p>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <Section background="base" padding="md">
    <Container narrow>
      <div class="space-y-12 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Lumina ERP ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website LuminaTech.xyz. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or engage with our ERP consulting services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Information You Provide</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            When you use our contact form, you may provide:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Company name</li>
            <li>Any additional information you include in your message</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Contact form submissions are processed through Formspree, a third-party form handling service. We do not store form data on our own servers.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            When you visit our website, certain information may be collected automatically, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li>Referring website</li>
            <li>Device information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide requested consulting services</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about our services</li>
            <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Our website uses the following third-party services:</p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Formspree</h3>
          <p>
            We use Formspree to process contact form submissions. When you submit a form, your data is transmitted to and processed by Formspree in accordance with their privacy policy.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Cloudflare</h3>
          <p>
            Our website is hosted and served through Cloudflare, which may collect basic analytics data and provides security services including DDoS protection. Cloudflare may set cookies for security and performance purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may use essential cookies required for basic site functionality and security (provided by Cloudflare). We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. Third-party services integrated into our site may set their own cookies as described in their respective privacy policies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Contact form submissions are retained by Formspree according to their data retention policies. We retain any personal information you provide via email or other communications for as long as necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected, or as required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Request access to any personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li>Opt out of any marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Our website is served over HTTPS, and we rely on Cloudflare's security infrastructure to protect data in transit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our website and services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Your continued use of the website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[length:var(--font-size-h2)] font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your data rights, please contact us:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Nick Brewer</span> -- Lumina ERP</li>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:Nickalus@LuminaResume.com" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">Nickalus@LuminaResume.com</a></li>
            <li>Location: Humble, TX</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

</BaseLayout>
